  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ninshi Masuta is a 2D action game, where you need to act fast and think like a ninja to keep yourself alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/b7d1b78e3ef84afa5b9e47e54c3743b3.poster.avif?t=1757975810\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/b7d1b78e3ef84afa5b9e47e54c3743b3.webm?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/b7d1b78e3ef84afa5b9e47e54c3743b3.mp4?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to face more than 20 levels and 8 bosses to free the city from criminals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/fdda79d3861e16f1c544a9f759af7742.poster.avif?t=1757975810\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/fdda79d3861e16f1c544a9f759af7742.webm?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/fdda79d3861e16f1c544a9f759af7742.mp4?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Incredible high resolution graphics running at 1080p and precise controls with fluent 60 frames per second.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use weapons like shurikens and grenades, in addition to your fists to defeat your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/47f37965a3ba48167bbde66ebb8ec48c.poster.avif?t=1757975810\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/47f37965a3ba48167bbde66ebb8ec48c.webm?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/47f37965a3ba48167bbde66ebb8ec48c.mp4?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Features</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ levels to beat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High resolution graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode for 2 simultaneous players locally</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound Test</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ninshi Masuta is a 2D action game, where you need to act fast and think like a ninja to keep yourself alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/b7d1b78e3ef84afa5b9e47e54c3743b3.poster.avif?t=1757975810\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/b7d1b78e3ef84afa5b9e47e54c3743b3.webm?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/b7d1b78e3ef84afa5b9e47e54c3743b3.mp4?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to face more than 20 levels and 8 bosses to free the city from criminals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/fdda79d3861e16f1c544a9f759af7742.poster.avif?t=1757975810\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/fdda79d3861e16f1c544a9f759af7742.webm?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/fdda79d3861e16f1c544a9f759af7742.mp4?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Incredible high resolution graphics running at 1080p and precise controls with fluent 60 frames per second.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use weapons like shurikens and grenades, in addition to your fists to defeat your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/47f37965a3ba48167bbde66ebb8ec48c.poster.avif?t=1757975810\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/47f37965a3ba48167bbde66ebb8ec48c.webm?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1249680/extras/47f37965a3ba48167bbde66ebb8ec48c.mp4?t=1757975810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Features</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ levels to beat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High resolution graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode for 2 simultaneous players locally</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound Test</p></li></ul>",
